    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2017 BMW M2 in the iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. The 19-inch forged wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with ample tread remaining. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with contrast blue stitching remains taut and supple, showing no signs of entry wear on the bolsters or thinning of the Alcantara door inserts. Every electronic feature, from the Harman Kardon premium sound system to the iDrive navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is stock and untouched, with only 11,500 original miles. It has a comprehensive service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers, with the most recent oil service and brake fluid flush completed just 200 miles ago. This is a collector-quality example for the enthusiast who demands perfection.",
