    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to see this one go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, and it's been garage-kept and meticulously maintained. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
