    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3, a hallmark of Bavarian engineering featuring the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six. This example is mechanically flawless, with a double-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile, short-throw shifts, while the M-Variable differential ensures exceptional lateral traction. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced and rod bearings replaced\u2014essential preventative measures for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing fresh bushings to maintain original turn-in precision. This collector-grade specimen is a turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
